= form.fields_for :participant_ten_item_attributes do |ten_item_f|
  %p.italic
    Please answer the following questions
    %span.underline about the personality of the person who referred you to this study.
  %h1 Ten-Item Personality Inventory
  %p
    Here are a number of personality traits that may or may not apply to the person who referred you
    to this study. Please write a number next to each statement to indicate the extent to which
    %span.underline
      you agree or disagree that the statement describes the person who referred you to this study.
  %p
    You should rate the extent to which the pair of traits applies to that person,
    even if one characteristic applies more strongly than the other.
  %ol
    %li Disagree strongly
    %li Disagree moderately
    %li Disagree a little
    %li Neither agree nor disagree
    %li Agree a little
    %li Agree moderately
    %li Agree strongly

  %p.italic
    I see the person who referred me to this study as:
  = render 'ten_item_questions', :ten_item_f => ten_item_f
